CustomField.description:
The meeting type:
0 — A prescheduled meeting. 1 — An instant meeting. 2 — A scheduled meeting. 3 — A recurring meeting with no fixed time. 4 — A personal meeting room. 7 — A PAC (Personal Audio Conference) meeting. 8 — A recurring meeting with a fixed time.
